  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Shingu: Secret of the Stellar Wars (学園戦記ムリョウ, Gakuen Senki Muryō; lit. \"Record of School Wars Muryou\") is an anime series directed by Tatsuo Sato and produced by Madhouse. Shingu aired from May 8, 2001, through December 4, 2001, on NHK. It ran for 26 episodes and was released on DVD on five volumes by The Right Stuf International in the United States.\nOn March 3, 2008, the series made its North American television debut on the Funimation Channel.",
